(0) READ-ITEM NUMBERS-IN PIVOT COMPARE END-OF-DATA GO TO OPERATION 1
(1) COMPARE PIVOT NUMBERS-IN IF LESS OR EQUAL GO TO OPERATION 2 OTHERWISE GO TO OPERATION 3
(2) TRANSFER NUMBERS-IN TO LEFT-PARTITION GO TO OPERATION 0
(3) TRANSFER NUMBERS-IN TO RIGHT-PARTITION GO TO OPERATION 0
(4) SORT LEFT-PARTITION RECURSIVELY
(5) WRITE-ITEM PIVOT
(6) SORT RIGHT-PARTITION RECURSIVELY
    INPUT NUMBERS-IN 3 6 8 10 1 2 1
    OUTPUT SORTED-NUMBERS
    END
